99
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:51,424
Kau bisa lihat lautan
dan segalanya!

100
00:09:51,508 --> 00:09:54,302
Jika kita beruntung,
mungkin kita akan melihat King Kong.

101
00:09:54,385 --> 00:09:55,845
