107
00:10:31,506 --> 00:10:34,175
<i>Kurasa aku akan
melunasinya suatu hari.</i>

108
00:10:40,098 --> 00:10:42,725
Apa ada kamar mandi
untuk pelanggan?

109
00:10:54,821 --> 00:10:56,906
