115
00:12:23,701 --> 00:12:24,869
Hei!

116
00:12:25,578 --> 00:12:27,330
Kataku, tak ada perilaku aneh!

117
00:12:27,413 --> 00:12:30,583
Ayo. Dua hari sewa!
